title: Disable unscoped global memory/search in profiled rooms
---
Acceptance: profiled room turns do not call unscoped Memory.search across all messages and do not inject raw global/core memories before scoped memory lands; compaction and memory flush paths do not reintroduce global reads; tests seed Channel A/B and prove no cross-channel prompt leakage. Files: src/agent.ml, src/agent_0_compact.ml, memory/search call sites, test/test_memory_search.ml, test/test_agent*.ml.